'''"Can't Stop the Shine"''' is the second single from American [[Hip hop music|hip hop]] artist [[Kool G Rap]]'s 1998 album ''[[Roots of Evil]]'', featuring [[Miss Jones (radio personality)|Miss Jones]].

==Background==
"Can't Stop the Shine" is a [[Mafioso rap]] song in which Kool G Rap spits two verses and features a chorus sung by [[Contemporary R&B|R&B]] singer [[Miss Jones (radio personality)|Miss Jones]].

==Music video==
The [[music video]] for "Can't Stop the Shine" shows Kool G Rap and Miss Jones partying on a lavish yacht, and Kool G Rap surviving as assassination attempt by two hitmen in his villa.

